      "description": "## What's New in 1.1.0\n\n### Documentation\n\n- Comprehensive JSDoc documentation added to all 16 source files\n- Module-level descriptions, function/class/interface docs, parameter and return docs\n- Security notes on escaping and sanitization points\n- Pipeline stage ordering explanations\n- Platform quirk documentation in profile files\n\n### Code Quality\n\n- Extracted duplicated `escapeHtml` function into shared `src/utils/html.ts` utility (CodeRabbit review feedback)\n- README badges: release version, CI status, license, CodeRabbit reviews, Ko-fi donation\n\n### Full Changelog\n\n**[1.0.1...1.1.0](https://github.com/canartuc/pubcopy/compare/1.0.1...1.1.0)**",
